    "name": "Shatterspike",
    "sources": [
      "Tales from the Yawning Portal p. 229"
    ],
    "text": "Versatile: This weapon can be used with one or two hands. A damage value in parentheses appears with the property — the damage when the weapon is used with two hands to make a melee attack.  Proficiency: martial, longsword",
