    "name": "Cold Weather Clothing",
    "sources": [
      "Icewind Dale"
    ],
    "text": "This outfit consists of a heavy fur coat or cloak over layers of wool clothing, as well as a fur-lined hat or hood, goggles, and fur-lined leather boots and gloves. As long as cold weather clothing remains dry, its wearer automatically succeeds on saving throws against the effects of extreme cold (see “Extreme Cold,” page 11).",
